dmca.title: Individual complains of blogged correspondence
dmca.body:
An email and a fax copy of this Notice and Takedown request are being sent to the fax and email addresses on file with the U.S. Copyright office for Google's designated agent to receive such notifications: 

To: [private]; [private]@google.com; fax: [private]


I have just been made aware of the URL http://cissplist.blogspot.com/ which web page contains, among many other documents, several of my copyrighted messages that are being reposted at this URL and without my permission. This is an infringement of my copyright.
